{
  "texts": [
    "DatasetWe utilize a raw clinical data source [4] called MIMIC-IV-Note [24], a compilation of 331,794 de-identified discharge summaries from 145,915 patients admitted to the Beth Israel Deaconess Medical Center.",
    "MIMIC-IV-Note [24] is a publicly available dataset reflective of real-world clinical notes.",
    "We pre-process MIMIC-IV [24] notes to create a labeled task-specific dataset, the MIMIC-IV-BHC [23] (Table 1), emphasizing the relationship between clinical notes and BHCs.",
    "Our open-source novel dataset is crucial to allow researchers to pursue further benchmarking studies.",
    "This study was institutional review board exempt because the MIMIC dataset does not meet the criteria for human subjects research described by our institution."
  ]
}